Source-Makefile: feeds/oldpackages/libs/libnfc/Makefile
Package: libnfc
Version: 1.7.0-1
Depends: +libc +USE_EGLIBC:librt +USE_EGLIBC:libpthread +libusb-compat +pcscd +ccid
Menu-Depends: 
Provides: 
Section: libs
Category: Libraries
Title: Near Field Communication (NFC) library
Maintainer: 
Source: libnfc-1.7.0.tar.bz2
Type: ipkg
Description:   libnfc is a free software library used to handle NFC capable devices.
  It supports the four main NFC modulations:
   * ISO14443-A (NXP MIFARE),
   * ISO14443-B,
   * JIS X 6319-4 (Sony Felica) and
   * Jewel Topaz (Innovision Research & Development).
  And depending on hardware, it supports:
   * Read (RFID @13.56Mhz),
   * Emulation and
   * Peer2Peer mode.
http://www.libnfc.org

@@

